For saas conversion
step one
remove comment in the models where
use App\Scopes\StoreIDScope;
and
 protected static function booted()
    {
        static::addGlobalScope(new StoreIDScope);
    }
now in controllers search for store_id
and remove comments where store_id exists
now in userRolesController.php
remove following line of code
->where('title','not like','Admin')

next search in vue files where store_id exists and remove comments from there as well
now next need to check seeder and migrations.
also check in database and supper admin exists and role for supper admin
next in user/Add.vue there will be field Store Domain: remove comment from that field
